Aim_kc_towers - v.1 - Made by: Danny Reall

This map was designed to improve players close-range skill. This is the second map ive ever made. I dont want people comparing it to maps like de_wanda etc. Its only for fun and training. Only provide feedback saying whats wrongand if you like it. I dont plan on editing the map for future releases though.

Note: in screenshots the map looks dark - this is because it took the screenshots from outside the skybox. Its medium brightness in-game
